<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font: 18.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Basic Theme</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Step 1</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">: Create a folder in "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941100;">/WordPressRoot/wp-content/themes/custom</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"WordPressRoot" - is the root installation folder of the WordPress</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"custom" - is the name of the folder where all my custom theme files will reside.</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Step 2</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">: Minimum requirements: </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Inside of the "custom"folder create two files </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #0433ff;">index.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">" </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #0433ff;">style.css</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">-------- index.php ----------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">&lt;h1&gt; This is my custom Theme &lt;/h1&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">-------------------------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Here is the minimum what you should have in the "style.css"</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">/*</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">Theme Name: MyCustomTheme</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">Author: Karshi Hasanov</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">Author URL: </span><a href="http://www.karshi.ca" style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">http://www.karshi.ca</a></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">Version: 1.0</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #797979;">*/</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">That's all !!!        You have just created a valid Theme</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Basic Theme</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> :</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">Print the Titles of the Posts</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Now we want our "index.php" talk to the </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic;">WordPress</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">: We want our code list all of the available Titles of the Posts.  </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">The</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;"> green colour </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> functions</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> are the </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic;">WordPress </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">builtin ones.</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">------- index.php -------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">if</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> (</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">have_posts()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">):</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">while</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> (</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">have_posts()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">): </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_post()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_title()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/h2&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">endwhile</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> endif</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">------------------------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Note: If you also want to print the content of a Post, just use the function </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_content()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">.</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Basic Theme</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">:</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;"> Make the Title have a Hyperlink</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">The function </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_permalink() </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">does the job:</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">…</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&lt;a</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> href="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_permalink()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">" </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;"></span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_title()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&lt;/a&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/h2&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">...</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Basic Theme:</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">Adding the header and footer</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Use the </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">get_header()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  and </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">get_footer()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  function to have the header and footer</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">--------- index.php --------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">   </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">get_header()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;     &lt;---------------  header goes here</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> if</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> (</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">have_posts()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">):</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">          </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> while </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">(</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">have_posts()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">): </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_post()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">   </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&lt;a</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> href="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">the_permalink()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;"> &gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;"> the_title()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/h2&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">   </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">endwhile</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> endif</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">   </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">get_footer()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;      &lt;---------------- footer  goes here</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">-------------------------------</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Intermediate Theme</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">Creating custom "header" and "footer" functions. </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">To that we need to create two files in our custom theme folder.</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">-------------- </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">header.php </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">-------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;html</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">language_attributes()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"></span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;head&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;meta charset="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">bloginfo('charset')</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">"&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;title&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">bloginfo('</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">name</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">')</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/title&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> wp_head(); </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/head&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;body</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">body_class()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"></span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&lt;a</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"> href="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">echo</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">home_url()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">"&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">bloginfo('</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">name</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">')</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">&lt;/a&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/h1&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h5&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">bloginfo('</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">description</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">')</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/h5&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">------------------------------------------</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">----------------</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> footer.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> -------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;footer&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;p&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">bloginfo('</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">name</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">')</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"> - &amp;copy;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">echo</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #009193;">date</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">('Y');</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/p&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/footer&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">wp_footer()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">; </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/body&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;/html&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">----------------------------------------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">Important: </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">You open the "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;html&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">,</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;body&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> and </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;div&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">" tags in the "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">header.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">" and don't forget</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">                 to close them in the "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">footer.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 19.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">How To add CSS style to the Custom Theme</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">There are two ways of adding a style sheet:</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">1.</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">As usual add the link to the Style Sheet in the &lt;head&gt; tag</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">2.</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">WordPress way of adding the Style Sheet. </span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">3.</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">We will be adding our style sheet by following the WordPress way. To do that we need to</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">introduce the </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">functions.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> file.</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">----------------- </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">functions.php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> ----------------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">function</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff;">KFH_resources()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> {</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #929000;">wp_enqueue_style</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">('style', </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">get_stylesheet_uri()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">);</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">}</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #929000;">add_action</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">('wp_enqueue_scripts', '</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">KFH_resources</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">');</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">--------------------------------------------------------</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">Note:</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> Because this is a pure PHP code, we don't close it with "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">".</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">Our style sheet called "</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">style.css</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">" and is created in the same folder where all other codes.</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">To make our style take an effect, we need to modify our "header.php" and "footer.php" so they use</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">the rules defined in CSS.</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">********* header.php ************</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">…</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;body</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">body_class()</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;"> ?&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"></span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">  &lt;div class="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff;">container</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #929292;">&lt;!--  site-header --&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;header</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;"> class="</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff;">site-header</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica;">"</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;"></span></div><div><span style="font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #531b93;">&lt;h1&gt;</span